CDK Data Module 0.3.0 API

A collection of APIs to simplify working with datasets in the Hadoop Distributed FileSystem (HDFS).

See:
          Description

Packages
com.cloudera.data Provides interfaces and classes for reading and writing datasets.
com.cloudera.data.crunch Provides helper classes for working with datasets using Crunch.
com.cloudera.data.filesystem Provides a dataset implementation for Hadoop filesystems, like HDFS.
com.cloudera.data.hcatalog Provides a dataset implementation that uses the Hive/HCatalog metastore for metadata, and stores data in a Hadoop FileSystem.
com.cloudera.data.partition Provides common implementations of FieldPartitioner.

 

A collection of APIs to simplify working with datasets in the Hadoop Distributed FileSystem (HDFS).

Unless explicitly stated otherwise, no methods this library accept or produce null values.
